1	Transfer student	Transfer student	Transfer student	Transfer student	Transfer student	/transfer-student	transfer-student	<p style="text-align:start"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri">Admission, Transfer, Reinstatement, and Dismissal Procedures and Rules for Study</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:start"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri">Admissions to higher education institutions are carried out based on the results of entrance exams (tests) conducted by the State Commission for Admission to Higher Education Institutions of the Republic of Uzbekistan according to the ranking system based on the collected scores.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:start"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri">Selection is conducted separately for each higher education institution based on the educational directions, teaching languages, and forms. In cases where targeted admission quotas are approved for certain directions in the regions, selection is carried out separately for each region.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:start"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri">Entrance exams are conducted by the State Testing Center under the Cabinet of Ministers of the Republic of Uzbekistan. Entrance exams are held in two languages - Uzbek and Russian. The teaching language in higher education institutions, admission quotas approved by the President of the Republic of Uzbekistan or the Cabinet of Ministers, and documents for admission within the framework of these quotas until the acceptance of documents are determined by ministries and agencies and approved by the State Commission. Applicants take entrance exams in the language of instruction at the higher education institution. Applicants who have submitted documents in Uzbek groups have the right to take entrance exams in Uzbek in Latin or Cyrillic alphabet based on their application.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:start"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri">Admission to General, Specialized, Specialized Secondary, and Evening Education:</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:start"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri">in the form of general education - based on the relevant document confirming the completion of general secondary (at the 10-11th grade level) or specialized secondary education and successful passage of entrance exams (tests);</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:start"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri">in the form of specialized secondary education - only on the basis of a certificate confirming secondary or specialized secondary education, in accordance with the field of specialization and education, based on the results of entrance exams (tests, written exam).</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:start"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri">Admission to General and Specialized Secondary Education:</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:start"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri">in the form of general education - based on the relevant document confirming the completion of general secondary (at the 10-11th grade level) or specialized secondary education and successful passage of entrance exams (tests);</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:start"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri">Admission of foreign citizens to higher education institutions is carried out in accordance with the Resolution No. 169 of August 4, 2008 of the Cabinet of Ministers of the Republic of Uzbekistan &quot;On Improving the Procedure for Admission to Study and Teaching in Higher Education Institutions of the Republic of Uzbekistan for Foreign Citizens&quot; and international agreements of the Republic of Uzbekistan.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:start"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri">Sending citizens of the Republic of Uzbekistan to study at foreign higher education institutions is carried out based on international agreements and the relevant decision of the State Commission, as well as with the support of citizens based on agreements with foreign educational institutions.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:start"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri">After the deadlines specified for registration of applicants, it is strictly forbidden to make changes and additions to the submitted documents.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:start"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri">If the authenticity of the submitted (completed) documents by the applicant is revealed, in this case, the applicant is disqualified from the entrance exams (if admitted to the higher education institution from the students) and the relevant authorities are informed about it in the specified order to protect the rights.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:start"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri">Applicants recommended for study on a fee-contract basis are enrolled in accordance with the terms specified in the contract each year. Contract forms similar to those specified are provided by the admissions committee of the higher education institution from the day the recommendation for admission to higher education institutions is announced, and are certified in three copies for legal entities and in 2 copies for individuals by the head and chief accountant.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:start"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri">Those dissatisfied with the decisions on admission to bachelor&#39;s degree programs of higher education institutions have the right to appeal to the ministries and agencies or in the established manner to the courts designated by the ministries.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<div id="gtx-trans" style="left:545px; position:absolute; top:41px">\r\n<div class="gtx-trans-icon">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>	<p>Talabalarni qabul qilish, ko&lsquo;chirish, qayta tiklash va o&lsquo;qishdan chetlashtirish tartibi va qoidalari.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Oliy ta&rsquo;lim muassasalarining kunduzgi, sirtqi va kechki bo&lsquo;limlariga talabalarni qabul qilish natijalariga ko&lsquo;ra to&lsquo;plangan ballarning reyting tizimi bo&lsquo;yicha O&lsquo;zbekiston Respublikasi ta&rsquo;lim tashkilotlariga qabul qilish bo&lsquo;yicha Davlat komissiyasi tomonidan amalga oshiriladi. kirish imtihonlari (testlar).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nTest sinovlari ta&rsquo;lim yo&lsquo;nalishlari, tillari va ta&rsquo;lim shakllari bo&lsquo;yicha har bir oliy ta&rsquo;lim muassasasi uchun alohida o&lsquo;tkaziladi. Agar qabul qilishning maqsadli standartlari mintaqalar bo&#39;yicha alohida hududlar uchun tasdiqlangan bo&#39;lsa, tanlov har bir mintaqa uchun alohida amalga oshiriladi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nTest sinovlari O&lsquo;zbekiston Respublikasi Vazirlar Mahkamasi huzuridagi Davlat test markazi tomonidan o&lsquo;tkaziladi. Test sinovlari ikki tilda &ndash; o&lsquo;zbek va rus tillarida o&lsquo;tkaziladi. Oliy ta&rsquo;lim muassasasida ta&rsquo;lim yo&lsquo;nalishlari bo&lsquo;yicha o&lsquo;qitish tili O&lsquo;zbekiston Respublikasi Prezidentining yoki Vazirlar Mahkamasining tegishli qarori bilan tasdiqlangan hamda Davlat komissiyasi tomonidan tasdiqlangan qabul kvotalari doirasida vazirlik va idoralar tomonidan belgilanadi. Abituriyent oliy ta&rsquo;lim muassasasida o&lsquo;qitiladigan til bo&lsquo;yicha test sinovlarini topshiradi. Bunda o&lsquo;zbek guruhiga ariza topshirgan abituriyent o&lsquo;z arizasiga asosan lotin alifbosida o&lsquo;zbek tilidan test sinovi topshirish huquqiga ega.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nSirtqi ta&rsquo;limga talabalarni qabul qilish:<br />\r\nsirtqi ta&#39;lim shaklida - kasb-hunar ta&#39;limi to&#39;g&#39;risidagi tegishli hujjatga ega bo&#39;lgan va sirtqi ta&#39;limga kirish imtihonlarini (imtihonlarini) muvaffaqiyatli tamomlaganlar hisobidan topshiriladigan umumiy o&#39;rta (10-11-sinflar negizida), o&#39;rta maxsus ta&#39;lim. trening. . ;<br />\r\nmaxsus sirtqi ta&#39;lim shaklida - faqat o&#39;rta maxsus ta&#39;lim, kasb-hunar ta&#39;limi va ta&#39;lim yo&#39;nalishi (o&#39;qituvchilik ishi) bo&#39;yicha tegishli yoki shunga o&#39;xshash ta&#39;lim yo&#39;nalishi, mutaxassisligi, kasbi bo&#39;yicha, mutaxassislik bo&#39;yicha kamida uch yillik amaliy tajribaga ega bo&#39;lgan holda. Lavozim. pedagogik yo&lsquo;nalishlar bo&lsquo;yicha ish tajribasi) va ular ishlayotgan soha bo&lsquo;yicha tashkilotlarning tavsiyanomalari kirish imtihonlarini (test, yozma imtihonlarni) muvaffaqiyatli topshirgan abituriyentlar hisobidan amalga oshiriladi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sirtqi va maxsus sirtqi bo&lsquo;limlarga talabalarni qabul qilish:<br />\r\nXorijiy fuqarolarni oliy ta&rsquo;lim muassasalariga o&lsquo;qishga qabul qilish O&lsquo;zbekiston Respublikasi Vazirlar Mahkamasining &ldquo;O&lsquo;zbekiston Respublikasining ta&rsquo;lim muassasalariga xorijiy fuqarolarni qabul qilish va o&lsquo;qitish tartibini takomillashtirish to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida&rdquo;gi avgustdagi qarori asosida amalga oshiriladi. 2008 yil 4-son va O&lsquo;zbekiston Respublikasining xalqaro shartnomalari.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nRespublika fuqarolarini xorijiy oliy ta&rsquo;lim muassasalariga o&lsquo;qishga yuborish davlatlararo shartnomalar va Davlat komissiyasining tegishli qarori, oliy ta&rsquo;lim muassasalari o&lsquo;rtasidagi shartnomalar hamda fuqarolar tashabbuslari asosida amalga oshiriladi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nAriza beruvchilarni royxatga olish muddati tugagandan song hujjatlarga ozgartirish va qoshimchalar kiritish qatiyan man etiladi.<br />\r\nAbituriyent tomonidan taqdim etilgan hujjatlar qalbakilashtirilganligi aniqlansa, abituriyent kirish imtihonlaridan (OTM talabalari o&lsquo;rtasida, agar u talabalikka qabul qilingan bo&lsquo;lsa) hamda huquqni muhofaza qilish organlaridan chetlashtiriladi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nTo&lsquo;lovli shartnoma asosida o&lsquo;qishga tavsiya etilgan abituriyentlar uchun to&lsquo;lov har yili shartnoma shartlarida belgilangan muddatlarda amalga oshiriladi. Ko&lsquo;rsatilgan namunadagi shartnoma shakllari oliy ta&rsquo;lim muassasalariga o&lsquo;qishga kiruvchilar uchun tavsiyanoma e&rsquo;lon qilingan kundan boshlab universitetning qabul komissiyasi tomonidan hamda yuridik shaxs rahbari va bosh buxgalter tomonidan 3 nusxada tuziladi. shuningdek 2 nusxada. . jismoniy shaxslar uchun.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nOliy ta&rsquo;lim muassasalariga o&lsquo;qishga qabul qilish to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi qarordan norozi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslar oliy ta&rsquo;lim muassasalarining vazirlik va idoralariga yoki sudga belgilangan tartibda shikoyat qilish huquqiga ega.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>	<p style="text-align:start"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri">Admission, Transfer, Reinstatement, and Dismissal Procedures and Rules for Study</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:start"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri">Admissions to higher education institutions are carried out based on the results of entrance exams (tests) conducted by the State Commission for Admission to Higher Education Institutions of the Republic of Uzbekistan according to the ranking system based on the collected scores.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:start"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri">Selection is conducted separately for each higher education institution based on the educational directions, teaching languages, and forms. In cases where targeted admission quotas are approved for certain directions in the regions, selection is carried out separately for each region.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:start"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font